5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Relating to firefighters; to amend Sections 11-43-144,
10 36-30-40, and 36-30-41, Code of Alabama 1975, to further
11 provide for disability and death benefits for firefighters; to
12 add Parkinson's disease to the list of firefighter's
13 occupational diseases; to provide a qualifying standard; and
14 to delete duplicative language and make nonsubstantive,
15 technical revisions to update the existing code language to
16 current style.
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
18 Section 1. Sections 11-43-144, 36-30-40, and 36-40-41,
19 Code of Alabama 1975, are amended to read as follows:
